Iran’s NIOC Names New Head of International Affairs, Shana Says

-- B y   L a d a n e   N a s s e r i
-- 
2011-04-06T07:38:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-06/iran-s-nioc-names-new-head-of-international-affairs-shana-says.html
Mohsen Qamsari was appointed as the
National Iranian Oil Co.’s new international affairs director,
Shana. the Oil Ministry’s official news website reported.  Qamsari will replace Ali Asghar Arshi,  Shana  said, citing a
statement by the company’s managing director Ahmad Qalebani. The
report did not give the reason behind the change.  Qamsari also serves as acting managing director for the
National Iranian Gas Export Co., Shana said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladane Nasseri in Tehran at 
 lnasseri@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  